  "summary": "Blueprint 简化摘要：共 87 个节点。\n执行入口：N12(Var SET P0), N13(Var SET P1), N18(K2Node_AddComponent), N2(Macro ForEachLoop), N25(K2Node_CallArrayFunction), N27(Call BoxComponent.SetBoxExtent), N36(Macro WhileLoop), N4(K2Node_CallArrayFunction), N40(Var SET guard), N45(Var SET step), N47(Macro WhileLoop), N48(Var SET SplineLength), N51(Var SET D1), N72(Var SET step), N76(Call KismetSystemLibrary.PrintString), N85(K2Node_AddDelegate)\n执行路径概览：\n- N12[Var SET P0] -> N13[Var SET P1] -> N72[Var SET step] -> N84[Var SET guardd]\n- N13[Var SET P1] -> N72[Var SET step] -> N84[Var SET guardd]\n- N18[K2Node_AddComponent] -> N85[K2Node_AddDelegate] -> N27[Call BoxComponent.SetBoxExtent] -> N25[K2Node_CallArrayFunction] -> N87[Var SET D]\n- N2[Macro ForEachLoop] -> {N3, N4}\n- N25[K2Node_CallArrayFunction] -> N87[Var SET D]\n- N27[Call BoxComponent.SetBoxExtent] -> N25[K2Node_CallArrayFunction] -> N87[Var SET D]\n节点细节（截断展示）：\n- N1: Var GET CollsionBoxes\n    outputs: CollsionBoxes:BoxComponent[] => N2.Array, N4.TargetArray\n- N2: Macro ForEachLoop\n    outputs: Array Element:BoxComponent => N3.self; Array Index:int\n- N3: Call ActorComponent.K2_DestroyComponent\n- N4: K2Node_CallArrayFunction\n- N5: Call SplineComponent.GetSplineLength\n    outputs: ReturnValue:real => N48.SplineLength\n- N6: K2Node_CommutativeAssociativeBinaryOperator\n    outputs: ReturnValue:real => N51.D1\n- N7: Call SplineComponent.GetLocationAtDistanceAlongSpline\n    outputs: ReturnValue:Vector => N12.P0\n- N8: Call SplineComponent.GetLocationAtDistanceAlongSpline\n    outputs: ReturnValue:Vector => N13.P1\n- N9: Var GET Spline\n    outputs: Spline:SplineComponent => N5.self\n- N10: Var GET Spline\n    outputs: Spline:SplineComponent => N7.self\n- N11: Var GET Spline\n    outputs: Spline:SplineComponent => N8.self\n- N12: Var SET P0\n    outputs: Output_Get:Vector\n- N13: Var SET P1\n    outputs: Output_Get:Vector\n- N14: K2Node_PromotableOperator\n    outputs: ReturnValue:Vector => N15.A\n- N15: K2Node_PromotableOperator\n    outputs: ReturnValue:Vector => N20.Start, N19.Location\n- N16: K2Node_PromotableOperator\n    outputs: ReturnValue:Vector => N17.A\n- N17: Call KismetMathLibrary.VSize\n    outputs: ReturnValue:real => N33.A\n- N18: K2Node_AddComponent\n    outputs: ReturnValue:BoxComponent => N25.NewItem, N27.self, N85.self\n- N19: Call KismetMathLibrary.MakeTransform\n    outputs: ReturnValue:Transform => N18.RelativeTransform\n- N20: Call KismetMathLibrary.FindLookAtRotation\n    outputs: ReturnValue:Rotator => N19.Rotation\n... 其余 67 个节点已省略。"
